message: Anyone here use a good jquery charting library?
These are also interesting: http://cyberpython.github.com/AwesomeChartJS/, http://www.rgraph.net/, http://code.google.com/p/flot/

@OyoKooN Yes, you're right! But I thought it's better to point to this fact to prevent him from disappointment ;-)
@marco_simon  @OyoKooN It is a commercial project but we are not against paying for good tools :) Looks to me so far that HighCharts fits what we want. Thanks guys.
